"\e[A": history-search-backward
"\e[B": history-search-forward
"\e[C": forward-char
"\e[D": backward-char
"\e\e[C": forward-word
"\e\e[D": backward-word

# https://www.topbug.net/blog/2017/07/31/inputrc-for-humans/
